data.description: Assumable 2.75% interest rate for the life of the loan, talk to your agent on how to make this work for you! Great layout in the split level home with lots of room! Upper level has an open concept with the kitchen/great room combo offering an island, SSA's, eat bar and fireplace, dining room has a slider to the covered back deck. Primary w/Ensuite, two additional bedrooms and a family hall full bath. Lower level has oversized family room w/fireplace, sewing room, two additional large bedrooms and a family hall bath, and a sewing room w/room for an office space as well and laundry room. Two car garage, large lot and room for garden area.
